-3441227">postpone their US East Coast tour</a> due to an unspecified “medical emergency.”</p><p> “We were so excited to play our first East Coast tour but sadly, due to a medical emergency, we will have to postpone to a later date,” they said. “All tickets will remain valid, so please hang on to yours for a moment while we work on rescheduled dates. If you prefer, a refund is possible — just reach out to your point of purchase. We can&#39;t wait to get out there and play and will announce new dates soon!”</p><p> The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/big-joanie-part-ways-with-drummer-due-to-differences-between-us-3510012">Big Joanie part ways with drummer due to “differences between us”</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
